parameters: \c[1]Welcome to my realm, Child.\! I have
watched you and your family closely.\! I
know where you have been, you will be and
where you are.\! My sight is beyond
\c[1]measure, it pierces the veil so only
truth remains. I see him, now.\! But not
as he was. . .\! And now, I see you.\! Your
curiosity is hereditary.\! I saw it in
\c[1]him, and now you.\! Come, child, I
will sate your hunger for knowledge.
